quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif – Laam – Raa. Woi yε Nwoma no mu nsεm no bi, ne Qur’aan a ԑda adi pefee no."
  15,2,"Mprε pii na wᴐn a wͻpo nokorε no bεpε sε na anka wͻyε Muslimifoͻ."
  15,3,"(Wodeε) gyae wͻn ma wͻnidi na wͻnye wͻn ani, na wͻma anidaasoͻ hunu nye wͻn adaagyeε na ԑnkyԑ wͻ’behunu."
  15,4,"Kuro biara a Yasεe no no, na εwͻ εberε a yahyε ato hͻ a yenim (sε yεde bεsεe no)."
  15,5,"Ɛmma sε ͻman bi betumi ama ne berε (a ͻsεeε bεba ne soͻ no) aba animu anaa akͻ akyire."
  15,6,"Deε wͻka ne sε: “Wo a yasiane Afutusεm (Qur’aan) yi ama woͻ no, nokorε sε wabͻ dam !”"
  15,7,"“Sε woka nokwafoͻ no ho ampa a, adεn nti na womma soro abͻfoͻ mma yεn hͻ?”"
  15,8,"Yε mma soro abͻfoͻ nnsiane, gyesε nokorε bi nti, na sε (soro abͻfoͻ ba wͻn hͻ a), εno deε wͻ nnya ahomegye berε."
  15,9,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na Yɛ sianee (Qur’aan) Afutusεm no, na nokorε sε, Yεn na Yεbεbͻ ho ban."
  15,10,"Ampa sε, Yε somaa asomafoͻ dii wanim kan kͻͻ tetefoͻ mmusua kuo no hͻ."
  15,11,"Ͻsomafoͻ a ͻbaa wͻn hͻ biara no gyesε wͻdi neho fεw."
  15,12,"Saa ara na Yεma (adwen bͻne) kͻwura abͻneεfoͻ no akoma mu-"
  15,13,"Wͻ nnye (Qur’aan) no nni, abrԑ a ampa sε tetefoͻ no (a wͻ’annye annie no) mfatoho bi abetwam."
  15,14,"Sε Yε bue ͻsoro pono ma wͻn na wͻ guso reforo kͻ mu mpo a,-"
  15,15,"Nokorε sε anka wͻ bεka sε: “Woi deε yaniso bri yεn. Daabi, Yε yε nnipa a yεde konya bi na anya yεn“."
